title: Bali bliss becomes nightmare as airlines hike up prices
text: Bali bliss becomes nightmare as airlines hike up prices Melanie Plane | 15th Jul 2015 6:28 AM Melanie Plane Journalist Hi! I’m your go-to reporter for sport, gossip and social media in Central Queensland. I’m a 20-year-old sports enthusiast who comes from a family of Aussie Rules players and cyclists. I am a former Queensland track cyclist and have been in the saddle for over 10 years now. I also play Aussie Rules and you can catch me doing a bit of CrossFit as well.
